\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}=\lvert\partial_{\mu}\Sigma\rvert^{2}+m^{2}\lvert\Sigma\rvert^{2}-\frac{\lambda}{4}\lvert\Sigma\rvert^{4}$
